<H3> <TI>   Smolensk Tax Inspectorate Cites 1993 Figures </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Smolensk Tax Inspectorate Cites 1993 Figures </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0490A Smolensk SMOLENSKIYE NOVOSTI in Russian 2 Mar 94 p 
