<H3> <TI>   Smolensk Oblast 1993 Statistics Cited </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Smolensk Oblast 1993 Statistics Cited </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944F0490B Smolensk SMOLENSKIYE NOVOSTI in Russian 15 Feb 94 
p 2 </F>

