<ABS>  FBIS Report: Central Eurasia </ABS>
<DATE1>   18 March 1994 </DATE1>
<F P=100> RUSSIA </F>
<F P=101> INTERNATIONAL AFFAIRS </F>
<H3> <TI>   Government Strategy on Foreign Investment Remains Unclear </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Government Strategy on Foreign Investment Remains Unclear </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0261B Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 18 Mar 94 p 4 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0261B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


