<H3> <TI>   Finance Ministry Reportedly Stalls Japanese Credits to </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Finance Ministry Reportedly Stalls Japanese Credits to </PHRASE></F></HT>


<TEXT>
Russian   Firms 

<F P=102> 944Q0248A Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 6 Mar 94 p 11 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0248A </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
