<H3> <TI>   Joint Venture Signs Agreement on Communications Satellites </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Joint Venture Signs Agreement on Communications Satellites </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0261A Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 18 Mar 94 p 1 </F>
