<H3> <TI>   Financing Scheme for Customs Committee Described </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Financing Scheme for Customs Committee Described </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944Q0249B Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY in Russian 6 Mar 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> 944Q0249B </F>
<F P=104>  Moscow KOMMERSANT-DAILY </F>
<F P=105>  Russian </F>


