<H3> <TI>   Caspian Consortium Structure Outlined </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Caspian Consortium Structure Outlined </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   944K0970B Almaty EKSPRESS-K in Russian 25 Mar 94 p 3 </F>
<F P=103> 944K0970B </F>
<F P=104>  Almaty EKSPRESS-K </F>
