<H5>  Quality of Consumer Goods </H5>
  In 1993, the Russian Federation State Inspection for Trade, 
Quality, and Consumer Rights Protection conducted 64,400 
inspections of consumer goods quality at industrial and trade 
enterprises; 62 percent of them resulted in finding the goods 
defective. 
